snippet: Suzann Pettersen, who is coming off two wins in her last three starts, birdied two of the last three holes for a six-under 66 and a share of the lead after the opening round of the season-ending Titleholders in Naples, Fla.
abstract: Suzann Pettersen, So Yeon Ryu and Sun Young Yoo share first-round lead at Titleholder's golf tournament, LPGA's season finale; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: Suzann Pettersen, who is coming off two wins in her last three starts, birdied two of the last three holes for a six-under 66 and a share of the lead after the opening round of the season-ending Titleholders in Naples, Fla.
